 2023 年播放次数最多的婚礼歌曲揭晓https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-most-played-wedding-song-of-2023-revealed-3561567?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-most-played-wedding-song-of- 2023-揭晓Tom SkinnerWed, 20 Dec 2023 08:36:56 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3561567 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新娘和新郎在婚礼上的第一支舞" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran)、阿黛尔 (Adele) 和约翰·传奇 (John Legend) 的曲目成为今年首支舞曲的热门选择</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-most-played-wedding-song-of-2023-revealed-3561567">《2023 年播放次数最多的婚礼歌曲》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新娘和新郎在婚礼上的第一支舞" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Top-WeddingSongs-2023-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2023 年英国播放次数最多的婚礼歌曲已揭晓。</p><p>根据<a href="https://encoremusicians.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Encore Musicians</a>的一项新研究， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ed-sheeran">Ed Sheeran</a>的 2017 年单曲“Perfect”是过去 12 个月来全国情侣特殊日子里最受欢迎的歌曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/best-songs-to-walk-down-the-aisle-to-wedding-2321885">婚礼歌曲：走在过道上最好听的歌曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>研究发现，今年英国 16% 的新婚夫妇在享受第一支舞时会播放<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/ed-sheeran-divide-album-review-2000538">“ <i>÷”</i> （“分水岭”）</a>曲目。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.clashmusic.com/news/ed-sheerans-perfect-was-the-most-played-wedding-song-in-2023/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Clash 报道</em></a>，Encore Musicians 将自己描述为“英国最大、最快的音乐家预订平台”，利用超过 3,000 场活动的基础来进行这项研究。</p><p>排在第二位和第三位的分别是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-legend">约翰·传奇</a>(John Legend) 的《All Of Me》(2013) 和猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">Elvis Presley</a> ) 的《Can&#39;t Help Falling In Love》(1961)。</p><p>希兰再次上榜，他 2014 年的民谣《Thinking Out Loud》排名第四。贾森·玛拉兹 (Jason Mraz) 的《我是你的》(I&#39;m Yours) (2008) 排名第五，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adele">阿黛尔 (Adele</a> ) 的《让你感受到我的爱》(Make You Feel My Love) (2008) 排名第六。</p><p>进入前十名的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/earth-wind-and-fire">Earth、Wind &amp; Fire</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/etta-james">Etta James</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruno-mars">Bruno Mars</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-wonder">Stevie Wonder</a> （来自<a href="https://www.express.co.uk/life-style/life/1846849/wedding-first-dance-songs-2023" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Express</em></a> ）的曲目。</p><p> 2023 年英国婚礼第一支舞最受欢迎的 10 首歌曲如下：</p><p> <strong>1) 艾德·希兰 – 《完美》</strong><br /> <strong>2) 约翰·传奇——《我的全部》</strong><br /> <strong>3) 埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 – 《情不自禁地坠入爱河》</strong><br /> <strong>4) 艾德·希兰 – 《大声思考》</strong><br /> <strong>5）杰森·玛拉兹——《我是你的》</strong><br /> <strong>6) 阿黛尔 – “让你感受到我的爱”</strong><br /> <strong>7) 土、风与火——“九月”</strong><br /> <strong>8) 埃塔·詹姆斯 – 《最后》</strong><br /> <strong>9）布鲁诺·马尔斯——《嫁给你》</strong><br /> <strong>10) 史蒂夫·旺德 – “她不是很可爱吗”</strong></p><p>最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/spotify-wrapped-2023-launches-worlds-most-streamed-artists-and-songs-3550716">Ed Sheeran 被 Spotify 评为 2023 年英国第五大流媒体音乐人</a>。这位创作型歌手在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-reveals-most-popular-artists-and-tracks-of-2023-3554559">TikTok 年度观看次数最多的艺术家排行榜</a>上也占据了同样的位置。</p><p>他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">艾尔顿·约翰 (Elton John)</a>合作的 2021 年节日单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/ed-sheeran-and-elton-john-new-song-merry-christmas-3110599">《圣诞快乐》</a>本月出现在<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/biggest-christmas-songs-21st-century/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方排行榜</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/top-40-biggest-christmas-songs-of-the-21st-century-revealed-3556523">“</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/top-40-biggest-christmas-songs-of-the-21st-century-revealed-3556523">21 世纪 40 首最热门圣诞歌曲”榜单</a>中。</p><p>希兰于九月发行了他最新的录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/ed-sheeran-autumn-variations-review-lyrics-tracklist-3505933">“Autumn Variations”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-most-played-wedding-song-of-2023-revealed-3561567">《2023 年播放次数最多的婚礼歌曲》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
